name: Universal Jet Enterprises
overview:
Universal Jet enterprises is a Partnership firm established in 2010. Our specialty lies in the trade, supply, export & wholesale of General Turning Tools, Milling Tools, Cutting Tools, Carbide Tools, Turning Tools, Drilling Tools, Industrial Boring Tools, Tool Holding Systems, Collet Chucks, Measuring Instruments, Threaded Inserts and Industrial Adapters.

Our Products: nternal Turning Tool Holders External Turning Tool Holders ISO Tungsten Carbide Threaded Inserts PCD Inserts Ceramic Inserts

Vendor Base: Our company is known for its strong bondage with its vendors who are our real assets. In order to satisfy the ever increasing demands and high expectations of our clients, we make sure to provide them the best finished products supplied by our valuable vendors.

Our Quality: Focusing on the agenda of “Providing the quality rather than quantity” is our objective. But our forte lies in maintaining quality along with quantity.

Client Satisfaction: Keeping in view the demands of our clients, we assure to provide them only quality based and tested products undergone through sophisticated filter process.

Why Us? We have become the first choice of the clients due to our consistent performance in terms of quality as well as quantity. Moreover, we have provided our clients with such a flexible range at variable price that it becomes almost impossible for the clients to have second choice other than us.
